
1.ForkTo your Account.Make a new branch in your name. 
2.Make three .txt files(applicant.txt, answers.txt, queries.txt)
3.applicant.txt should contain a link to your resume, your phone number and email address. 
4.answers.txt should contain your answers.
5.In queries.txt, you can ask us what queries you have.
6.Request for a Pull.
7.If selected we shall let you know about a second meeting. 
